<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/45000121/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription "The evaluation would be continuous by default. In the evaluation, we will check if the students have achieved the competences related to the topic. In the continuous evaluation we will use written exams (EX), Individual work (TI) and Group work (TG). For direct evaluation, not following the continuous evaluation, students will have to pass a single written exam in English. This exam will evaluate the same capacities as the continuous evaluations."@es .

